description: Triple Jay's Pizza is taking America's favorite meal on the move, and the foodies of Georgia could not be happier! This cool crew is taking their pizzas straight to the streets- and serving up these delicious pies buffet-style! You're sure to find all these toppings to be completely tasty-Pepperoni, Chicken Alfredo, Buffalo Chicken, BBQ, and Jerk too!Make your way to Triple Jay’s for wonderful pizza that will make your day!
name: Triple Jay's Pizza
